content:
Engagement Data Retention and Access Policy Is Changing. 
Beginning on January 15, 2025, the retention period for send and engagement data is limited to 180 days. This policy applies to data that you retrieve using Email Studio, Analytics Builder, tracking extracts in Automation Studio, or SOAP API. Data that exceeds this retention period is deleted. If your contract is dated before April 10, 2024, your data is retained indefinitely, but the new retention policy is applied on the next contract renewal date. If your contract is dated April 10, 2024 or later, we retain the data for up to 180 days.

This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.
title: Marketing Cloud Engagement Data Retention Policy Change
